query:
SELECT 
  id,
  task_id,
  title,
  duration,
  CASE 
    WHEN duration IS NULL THEN '❌ NULL'
    WHEN duration = 0 THEN '❌ 0 秒'
    WHEN duration <= 60 THEN '✅ ≤60 秒'
    ELSE CONCAT('❌ ', duration, ' 秒 (超過限制)')
  END as status,
  created_at
FROM podcast_highlights
ORDER BY created_at DESC
LIMIT 20;
